  "text": "28th June, 2002 Notification No. 42/2002 - Customs (N.T.) In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-rule (1) of rule 3 of the Customs Tariff (Transitional Product Specific Safeguard Duty) Rules, 2002, the Central Government hereby appoints Shri R. K. Gupta, Commissioner of Customs (General), New Delhi as the Director General (Specific Safeguard) for the purposes of the said rules. Dhirendra Singh Garbyal Under Secretary to the Government of India F. NO. - 526/6/2002 - CUS(T.U.) -- 1 of 1 --",
